04:05.389 --> 04:07.007
Sit.

04:14.599 --> 04:17.966
I have been contemplating
our circumstances, Michael,

04:18.019 --> 04:21.654
and I'm deeply concerned
by what you've done.

04:21.738 --> 04:23.773
I have questions,
important questions,

04:23.824 --> 04:28.361
questions that will determine
your future...

04:28.446 --> 04:30.080
and ours.

04:30.147 --> 04:31.865
What do you want to know?

04:31.949 --> 04:34.334
I need to know
exactly what the CIA wants.

04:34.418 --> 04:36.419
They want the leader
of this group.

04:36.487 --> 04:39.589
They want you.
Hmm.

04:39.657 --> 04:40.897
And if you
don't give them that?

04:40.925 --> 04:43.126
My friends will spend
the rest of their lives

04:43.177 --> 04:45.095
a CIA detention center.

04:49.183 --> 04:53.937
What we do here together...

04:54.004 --> 04:56.690
What we stand for...

04:56.774 --> 04:58.108
Do you believe in it?

04:58.175 --> 05:00.843
And don't...

05:00.895 --> 05:02.896
Give me the answer
that you think I want.

05:02.980 --> 05:06.866
What I want is the truth.

05:06.951 --> 05:09.519
I haven't always agreed
with your methods,

05:09.570 --> 05:12.872
but the jobs
I've helped you with,

05:12.957 --> 05:16.242
the ones no one else
was willing to do,

05:16.327 --> 05:18.662
they needed to be done.

05:18.713 --> 05:22.215
We protect what is important.

05:22.300 --> 05:23.800
You made me part of something

05:23.867 --> 05:27.253
that's bigger than you,
bigger than me.

05:27.338 --> 05:30.840
You made me believe there is
something worth fighting for,

05:30.891 --> 05:32.258
something to believe in.

05:35.179 --> 05:38.381
I believe in you,
Michael Westen.

05:38.432 --> 05:40.049
Always have.

05:42.436 --> 05:45.105
I think
there's a way out of this,

05:45.189 --> 05:47.490
a way to salvage
our organization,

05:47.558 --> 05:51.611
a way to save your friends,
a way to save yourself.

05:51.696 --> 05:55.732
But in order to do that, I need
you to do something for me.

05:55.783 --> 05:58.201
I need you to go
back to Miami

05:58.252 --> 06:02.505
and return yourself
to the good graces of the CIA.

06:02.573 --> 06:06.509
I need you to tell them
a story.

06:06.577 --> 06:09.846
I need you to convince them
that you barely escaped with us

06:09.913 --> 06:12.932
after the mission went wrong.

06:13.017 --> 06:15.418
I need you to convince them
that you looked

06:15.469 --> 06:17.420
for an opportunity
to capture me yourself,

06:17.471 --> 06:20.523
you moved heaven and earth
to complete your task,

06:20.591 --> 06:22.776
but it proved impossible.

06:26.096 --> 06:29.866
And I need you
to convince them

06:29.933 --> 06:33.370
that you made me believe
I was betrayed by an underling,

06:33.437 --> 06:37.290
and you have heroically returned
home to continue your work.

06:40.411 --> 06:41.944
Will you do that?

06:45.633 --> 06:47.667
Will you lie
to the CIA for me?

06:55.676 --> 06:57.627
Jesus, Michael!

06:57.678 --> 06:58.845
We thought you were dead.

06:58.929 --> 07:00.797
Yeah, I'm in Mexico.
I'm fine.

07:00.848 --> 07:03.266
Good.

07:03.317 --> 07:06.903
And the operation?

07:06.970 --> 07:09.439
My cover is intact.

07:09.490 --> 07:11.362
The operation is still alive.

07:11.387 --> 07:15.387
